FBIS4-59372 "drnes093_k_94003" FBIS-NES-94-093 Daily Report 12 May 1994 IRAQ Defense Minister Allegedly Executes 5 Citizens Defense Minister Allegedly Executes 5 Citizens NC1205160794 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution in Arabic 1430 GMT 12 May 94 NC1205160794 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution in Arabic 1430 GMT 12 May 94 Arabic BFN [Text] The criminal 'Ali Hasan al-Majid, tyrant Saddam's defense minister, has executed five citizens from the region of (al- Sahafi). He shot them in front of a group of leaders of the Sixth Armed Company. Eyewitnesses have affirmed that he decorated a number of the officers of that company for bravery for following his orders to the letter.
